      • convertToStringWalksDuplicateFree

        public static List<String> convertToStringWalksDuplicateFree(List<List<String>> dataStructureToConvert)
        Given a list of walks where a walk is represented as a List of strings, this method will convert that into a list of strings where a walk is one string (and the elements are separated by spaces). The lists are duplicate free.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        Data structure converted to string list.
